{"word":"προσεργάζομαι","slug":"προσεργάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσεργάζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-άσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to work in addition to</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>; <el>ἀγαθὰ πρ. τινι</el> <i>to do</i> good <i>service to</i> one <i>besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to make</i> or <i>earn in addition</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}